      • LdapPingRequest

        public LdapPingRequest(String hostName,
                       Set<NetlogonNtVersion> ntVersion)
        Constructs a minimal LDAP ping request.
        Parameters:
        hostName - the name of the host to which the request will be sent (target server)
        ntVersion - the Netlogon NT version flags for the target server
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if hostName is null or ntVersion is null
        IllegalArgumentException - if hostName is empty
